         <children>
            <Label layoutX="14.0" layoutY="14.0" text="This is a simple event management system.It has been made using JAVA and JAVAFX.&#10;On the extreme left of the screen is navigation bar .&#10;1)Top most button has &quot;Home &quot; written on it .&#10;&#9;It will take you to Home section of the app where you can look at our venues and past management events.&#10;2) Next from top is New Booking. &#10;&#9;On clicking this button you will be redirected to a page where you can make a new booking for your event.&#10;3)Next from top is button for My Account page. &#10;&#9;On clicking this you will see information related to your account on display. &#10;&#9;You can also search data about various customers and their events.&#10;4)On clicking the Booking History button of the navigation bar, &#10;&#9;you will see a screen that displays information about all past event bookings from our app.&#10;5)Next is the change Password page .&#10;&#9;You can click on this if you want to change password of your account.&#10;6)Next is the About US button.&#10;&#9;On clicking this button you wil see information about the creaters of this system diaplayed on he screen.&#10;7)Next is the Help Button which will take you to this page.&#10;8)After Help comes the Logout button. &#10;&#9; On clicking this button you will be shown a screen where you will be asked to confirm if you want to logout.&#10;&#9;On confirmation you will logout and will be shown the login screen.&#10;9)At the end is the exit button.&#10;&#9;On clicking this button you will be shown a sceen where you wil be asked to confirm if you want to exit.&#10;&#9;On confirmation you will exit the system." textFill="#195190">
